    "Participant 6",
    "The above excerpt highlights that postgraduate students engaged in historically disadvantaged universities in South Africa utilise ChatGPT for editing and paraphrasing their academic research, specifically for their master's studies.",
    "This observation aligns with the findings of Imran and Almusharraf (2023) and Day (2023), who assert that ChatGPT aids students in producing high-quality work by offering support in the editing process.",
    "Additionally, the current study emphasises the significant utility of ChatGPT as an AI tool for postgraduate students, particularly in enhancing their academic writing skills through effective paraphrasing.",
    "Sallam (2023) further affirms that ChatGPT plays a crucial role in ensuring that postgraduate students generate research that is free from poor sentence construction."
  ],
